{"tid":998984,"cid":27,"subCid":0,"title":"後日有冇人有興趣上深圳打邊爐","createTime":"2019-01-28T11:21:26.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-28T13:35:47.000Z","uid":78044,"like":1,"dislike":20,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"dd09cf42b6834dd3115aa6507d30c1f78258f72f","tid":998984,"uid":78044,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-28T11:21:26.000Z","msg":"是咁的<br />\n<br />\n我見到couchsurfing 個網站，有人搞左個晚餐聚會。<br />\n<br />\n心旭旭想去，但又想搵人陪。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.couchsurfing.com/events/oct-language-exchange-shenzhen-shi-2019-01-30\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.couchsurfing.com%2Fevents%2Foct-language-exchange-shenzhen-shi-2019-01-30&d=L9WWkC8qCnSwgTnBr0z%2BTAhMEkA7P3Wv%2FuCJwdwWxT4%3D&h=30f1fda7\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.couchsurfing.com/events/oct-language-exchange-shenzhen-shi-2019-01-30</a><br />\n<br />\nOCT Language Exchange<br />\n\r<br />\nWe believe that learning new language is not only about the language itself, it is about being immersed into a culture and experiencing everything it has to offer.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nCouchsurfing OCT Language exchange is a close community where you can share your story and meet some interesting friends.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nFor every first Wednesday of each month we are going to explore a new restaurant for dinner. We share the bill AA style. <br />\r\nFor every third Wednesday of each month we will invite one friend to share his/her travel experience. If you would like to share yours, WELCOME!!!<br />\r\nThe rest Wednesday of each month we will have regular meetups with a topic. Everyone is welcome to host the event. Feel free to contact me if you have a good idea to talk and share. (Please note the topics can&rsquo;t be about politics or sex)<br />\r\n<br />\r\nFee: It&rsquo;s a free event, but please kindly order something from the caf&eacute; to show our appreciation. 10% for everyone. <br />\r\n<br />\r\nIf you have any questions, please feel free to contact Gaily and Joan <br />\r\nGaily&rsquo;s Wechat: gailyzeng<br />\r\nJoan 's Wechat: Joanzmz<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncy.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a6f2e53ee23e904478f2884614431da99a45d8d8","tid":998984,"uid":78044,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-28T11:40:22.000Z","msg":"Topic：Annual Dinner party-Sichuan hot pot. Let&rsquo;s gathering together to enjoy the Sichuan food. Welcome to join us. The sign up deadline is on Wednesday 1pm.&nbsp;<br />\nPlease sign up through WECHAT in advance. It&rsquo;s easier for us to make a reservation. Otherwise we can&rsquo;t guarantee that there will be enough seat for you.<br />\nHost: Gaily&nbsp;<br />\nWechat: gailyzeng&nbsp;<br />\nDate: January 30th 19:00&nbsp;<br />\nLocation: houhai metro station exit E<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 推"},{"pid":"f831ad94f8d11f2a60bc72a81a808ef2f75390c8","tid":998984,"uid":223963,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-28T11:46:11.000Z","msg":"深圳咁遠<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e926b35a05d2e7b0462524aab5fbbdcceecfaf01","tid":998984,"uid":78044,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f831ad94f8d11f2a60bc72a81a808ef2f75390c8","tid":998984,"uid":223963,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-28T11:46:11.000Z","msg":"深圳咁遠<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-28T11:48:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"794f0e6880f74aeda30155b55bbd000d2daeffdf","tid":998984,"uid":78044,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-28T12:16:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/36.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e5ac1b7e01f616312e3f368d6704a8d849b0ec76","tid":998984,"uid":70121,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-28T12:23:53.000Z","msg":"會唔會上左去落